data.description: Welcome home to this lovely, practically brand new, 4 bedroom PLUS a study, situated in Deer Creek school district! This lovely modern farmhouse in the Northbrook Addition was just built in 2021. With wood look tile through the common spaces, a large great room with open kitchen, large dining, and living spaces, this home was designed for entertaining. The split floor plan offers privacy with the primary suite located at the front of the home, and all other bedrooms at the back. Right off the entry is the office, which could also be used as a play room, workout room, or just an additional hangout space. You'll love the kitchen with it's large island, ample pantry, farmhouse sink, and upgraded lighting fixtures. The 3 secondary bedrooms have good sized closets, and the full bath next to those rooms boasts a separate vanity area from the bathroom. Top it all off with a darling front porch and covered patio in the back, and this home checks all the boxes!
